main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 3201/90 is amended as follows:
(a) the following indent is added to Article 13(2)(b): "- Canada, if described by the term 'Icewine'.";
(b) the following indent is added to Article 13(3)(a): "- Canada, if described by the term 'Icewine'.";
(c) the following Chapter is added after "Chapter 3a Australia" in Annex I: "4. CANADA
- 'Icewine', possibly with the term 'VQA' or the words 'Vintners Quality Alliance'."
